abstract: But does she have Trump’s number? And what is going on with him anyway?
snippet: But does she have Trump’s number? And what is going on with him anyway?
lead_paragraph: Bret Stephens: Hi, Gail. Did you read our friend Frank Bruni’s column this past weekend? It’s one of the most thought-provoking articles I’ve read in a while about the likely shape of the 2020 race, and it contains this fascinating nugget: “19 Republicans in Congress have already announced that they won’t seek another term in their current office,” and most of them are just retiring from politics altogether instead of seeking a higher office.
